[id="GetMyReportHistory_{context}"]
= GetMyReportHistory

:toc: macro
:toc-title:

toc::[]


`GET /v2/reports/configurations/{id}/my-history`

GetMyReportHistory returns the requester's report job history for a report configuration with the specified ID.
